\f0\b\fs64 \cf6 A Quick Look at Grunt in Action}}
\b\fs64 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl540\sa600

\b0\fs32 \cf2 Let\'92s say you wanted to check for errors in your JavaScript file. After you have setup Grunt, just run\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl400

\f2\fs28 \cf7 \cb8 \shad\shadx0\shady-20\shadr0\shado0 \shadc0 $ grunt jshint \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl540\sa600

\f0\fs32 \cf2 \cb3 \shad0 and you will see the errors in your JavaScript files!\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl440\sa600
{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://scotch.io/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/grunt-jshint.png"}}{\fldrslt 
\f3\fs24 \cf0 }}\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl540\sa600
