\f0\b\fs64 \cf6 Making This Super Simple}}
\b\fs64 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl540\sa600

\b0\fs32 \cf2 There are many tutorials out there that talk about the great things you can do with Grunt. While great, sometimes they come with confusing and fully fledged configurations that are hard to understand for someone just getting into Grunt.\
This will be 
\b a guide in the basics of using Grunt
\b0  and creating an incredibly simple and easy setup to handle the tasks mentioned above. This setup will teach us the basics but will let us think how we can expand Grunt for future more advanced uses.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl480
{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://scotch.io/bar-talk/a-simple-guide-to-getting-started-with-grunt#getting-started"}}{\fldrslt 
